# init(undefined:)

**Initializer**

Creates an undefined feature value of a specific type.

## Declaration

```swift
init(undefined type: MLFeatureType)
```

## Creating a sendable feature value

- **init(_:)**: Creates a feature value containing a double-precision floating-point value.
